{"tid":409793,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"北海道知床漁場 大阪最垃圾既餐廳","createTime":"2017-09-22T11:11:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T05:42:46.000Z","uid":20967,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6d6a889b338d0416556560cacad37493f499e6","tid":409793,"uid":20967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"我家姐上網睇到 唔知邊度介紹生蠔，蟹任食<br />\n一黎到就叫我地食套餐，<br />\n咁叫左最貴果個5980/一人<br />\n一開始會黎左堆比你食既，跟住食完可以比你再叫其他餐牌上規定既<br />\n<br />\n頂，啲生蠔都好啲，蟹就垃圾既，食落去梅既同冇冇肉既，跟住叫第二，第三次既都等勁耐，差唔多成3 4個字催十幾次都未黎，成個餐廳得一個講國語既staff，其他架仔西哂面咁，個國語staff係咁話唔好意思，但又係咁等都未到，頂 食2個鐘仲話最後半個鐘last order，差啲谷鬼氣走人。<br />\n<br />\n勸大家唔好食依間 垃圾到。"},{"pid":"978e30608f61bc1e6ab9068e4dad88098357308f","tid":409793,"uid":9231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:12:26.000Z","msg":"又係隱世整邪惡？"},{"pid":"2a0aa79166db8fab4cd9452ead73319a2efe7ac1","tid":409793,"uid":14135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:13:38.000Z","msg":"大阪食蟹緊係去網元本館啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d41f93666e308a5b37be87b35e2ba6322539e40","tid":409793,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"好貴wor<br />\n多唔多人食？"},{"pid":"885343b3473598efa72f40eab739700a36700586","tid":409793,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"想講普通話就去大阪啦<br />\n北海道邊係你外地人去架"},{"pid":"6d34b004daafe32ae42090cc54297b8172ec7cc0","tid":409793,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大阪食蟹緊係去網元本館啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪就係， 都唔洗諗"},{"pid":"5d627d5dd624f3d2e19b88559e4228d272466eca","tid":409793,"uid":20967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T11:21:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好貴wor<br />\n多唔多人食？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全部本地人居多<br />\n擺明屈外地人"},{"pid":"bd0